lead_paragraph: Federal prosecutors want a Miami judge to reduce by more than a year the four-year prison sentence being served by Anthony Bosch, the former owner of the clinic.

headline.print_headline: US Seeks Sentencing Cut for Baseball Drug Clinic Owner
